raph" style="text-align:start;"><b>想阅读更多内容吗？</b></p><p class="paragraph" style="text-align:start;">请参阅<a class="link" href="https://www.newsminimalist.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">newsminimalist.com</a>上的其他新闻。</p><hr class="content_break"><p class="paragraph" style="text-align:start;">感谢您阅读我们的文章，明天见，</p><p class="paragraph" style="text-align:start;">瓦迪姆</p></div><div class='beehiiv__footer'><br class='beehiiv__footer__break'><hr class='beehiiv__footer__line'> <a target="_blank" class="beehiiv__footer_link" style="text-align: center;" href="https://www.beehiiv.com/?utm_campaign=1c583ac8-7873-478a-9451-cfceb8e0b761&utm_medium=post_rss&utm_source=news_minimalist_daily">技术支持：beehiv</a></div></div> ;
